data.description: Country Home for Sale in Southern Missouri!3.5 Acres m/l with 3 bedroom, 2 bath Ranch-style home with a large covered front porch with a great view! This home has a great living area and kitchen with island.There is a detached workshop, a large yard with gently rolling terrain, and an abundance of wildlife. Located just outside of Hartville, Missouri with a private country setting.  Enjoy the countryside and small town living. NO RESTRICTIONS.
